fulltitle: Bob Berg - Five of My Favorite Recordings
description: From a 1998 interview with Bret Primack, Bob Berg (1951-2002) talks about his favorite recordings from John Coltrane, Bela Bartok, Frank Sinatra, Art Blakey and Miles Davis.
title: Bob Berg - Five of My Favorite Recordings
